OpenShift Container Adoption

Technology Stack

Angular UI, .NET Core API, Oracle Database

SSO Login, Friendly URLs


Key Features

Routing: Ingress & SSL Routes with Certificate Manager

CI/CD: S2I Builds, Jenkins Pipelines with Ansible Playbooks

Monitoring & Logging: Dynatrace for performance, Splunk for logs


Benefits

Scalable, secure, and automated deployments

Faster delivery with streamlined pipelines

Real-time monitoring and centralized log analysis


Workflow

1. Develop Angular & .NET Core API


2. Automate builds and deployments via OpenShift


3. Secure traffic with SSL routes


4. Monitor with Dynatrace & analyze logs with Splunk



Impact

Improved performance, security, and operational efficiency
